data.title: Alexander III, Emperor of Russia, Maria Feodorovna, Empress of Russia, Queen Alexandra and Grand Duchess Olga Alexandrovna
data.meta_description: Photograph of Alexander III, Emperor of Russia (1845-94), Maria Feodorovna, Empress of Russia (1847-1928), Queen Alexandra (1844-1925) and Grand Duchess Olga Alexandrovna (1882-1960). Alexander III is standing to the left holding a walking stick in his left hand. Maria Feodorovna is standing beside him to the right, her right hand on his shoulder. Queen Alexandra and Grand Duchess Olga are standing to the right, both holding wicker baskets. An open door and part of a garden can be seen behind them. The...
